(43, 13, 11, 43, 2, 25, 25, 'he knew who should betray him', 'Knowledge of Betrayal and Humanity', 'Both passages emphasize Jesus'' profound understanding of human nature. In John 13:11, He knows who will betray Him, while in John 2:25, it states He knew what was in man.', 'theme', 0.321, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
